DTEND:20260527T220000
SUMMARY:18+ Figure Drawing: May Session
LOCATION:Unkindness Art\, 2923 North Avenue\, Richmond\, VA 23222
DESCRIPTION:Ongoing nude figure drawing series open to artists 18+. Long pose session featuring a single model. Tickets must be purchased in advance\; space is limited. Valid photo ID required at door.\\n\\nCost: $10.00\\n\\nRegister: https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-may-2026
URL:https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-may-2026
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-05-28-1800-studiotwothree@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260525T122322Z
DTSTART:20260528T180000
DTEND:20260528T210000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing - 5/28
LOCATION:Studio Two Three\, 109 W 15th St Richmond\, VA 23224
DESCRIPTION:3-hour figure drawing workshop with professional nude model. Instructor Carter Helmandollar calls poses\, starting with short gestural poses and building to longer poses. Artists bring own materials\; extra paper\, pencils\, and clipboards available.\\n\\nCost: $20.00\\n\\nRegister: https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-528
URL:https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-528
END:VEVENT
